714440f-a.title: Manhattan: 75th Street (East) - York Avenue
714440f-a.text:
East 75th Street, south side, east from York (Ave. A.) Ave., to the
East River. Prominent building shown is the Power House of the I.R.T. Co.
Segtember 15, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
